name: Mirage
description: What do you see in times of desperation? What do you see when your eyes have been staring at a screen with no rest and you're dehydrated? This piece exhibits the mirage (created by AI), encased in your retina and your retina is vibrantly shutting down. No rest for the weary. Guide us, AI, but not toward that which is only illusion. Unclaimed to be burned after HEN500K.
